  <summary date="2019-02-01T19:52:17Z" status="Introduced in House">Tax Free Health Insurance Act of 2019

This bill allows an individual taxpayer a deduction from gross income for insurance premiums paid for the health care coverage of the taxpayer and the taxpayer's spouse and dependents. The bill makes the deduction available whether or not the taxpayer itemizes other deductions.</summary>
